fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/133609/', '', 'Amisulpride, Lumateperone, Pimavanserin', 'Perphenazine', 1767369485);
